channel.description:
[size=36pt]RuneWings317![/size] Cmon guys! 600 views and only 18 posts? Lets start posting please so I can improve! ~Credits: XLdarkwingLX, JJ, X bow X and locksmin (Original source maker) ~Version: 1.0 ~Info: This is my first source! Please be gracious! Also please don't leach... If your going to please give me credit! I do [color=red][u][b]NOT[/b][/u][/color] give permission to post on other sites!
Making a v1.1! (NOT v2!)
~[u]Client Download[/u]~ [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?o26n84wva8psbdn]http://www.mediafire.com/?o26n84wva8psbdn[/url]
~[u]Source Download[/u]~ [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?yx2z92xrhxd4t4a]http://www.mediafire.com/?yx2z92xrhxd4t4a[/url]
[center]~[u]Things in the Source[/u]~[/center] [center]Full GodWars Dungeon (Animated bosses AND drops!) My own custom training zone A custom dungeon I made Pest Control, Kalphite Queen, Ice Queen, Giant Moles, KBD Lunar, Ancient and Normal Magic 4 quests All skills working God Sword Stances and Specials! Dragon Claw specials! Cool Customs (Dragon Plate Body, Dragon Kite Shield, and more) Working Equipment Screen[/center]
~[u]Pictures[/u]~ Welcome [img]http://i20.servimg.com/u/f20/15/50/61/08/runewi11.jpg[/img]
GodWars dungeon! [img]http://i20.servimg.com/u/f20/15/50/61/08/runewi10.jpg[/img]
Home [img]http://i20.servimg.com/u/f20/15/50/61/08/runewi12.jpg[/img]
Skiller Zone Area 1 [img]http://i20.servimg.com/u/f20/15/50/61/08/runewi13.jpg[/img]
Skiller Zone Area 2 [img]http://i20.servimg.com/u/f20/15/50/61/08/runewi14.jpg[/img]
Training Zone [img]http://i20.servimg.com/u/f20/15/50/61/08/runewi15.jpg[/img]
Equipment Screen [img]http://i20.servimg.com/u/f20/15/50/61/08/runewi16.jpg[/img]
Well I hope you like it! My next release will be my current source! Please comment! And if someone finds the original maker of this source please tell me so I can add him to the credits list! Thanks guys! Please also tell me if I missed something!
Please comment and tell me how I did! But please, no crap!
©XLdarkwingLX
